    "description": "<p>When you Cast a Spell that targets an Area of Effect, you can choose to protect some of the creatures from the spell’s full force. </p><p>Spend <strong>1 MP</strong> and choose a number of creatures up to your <strong>Prime</strong> <strong>Modifier</strong>.</p><p>All chosen creatures automatically succeed on any <strong>Saves</strong> against the Spell, and have <strong>Resistance</strong> to any damage dealt by it. </p><p>Alternatively, you can spend <strong>2 MP</strong> instead to make the chosen creatures immune to the Spell’s damage and effects.</p>",
